<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Two Dee Engineering - Precision Engineering</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #ffffff 50%, #f1f5f9 100%);
            color: #0f172a;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        
        /* Navigation */
        .navbar {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 20px 40px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            z-index: 1000;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(44,94,46,0.1);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
        }
        
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 800;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2C5E2E 0%, #800020 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
        
        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 30px;
        }
        
        .nav-links a {
            color: #334155;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }
        
        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: #2C5E2E;
        }
        
        /* Admin Link Button */
        .admin-link {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2C5E2E, #800020);
            color: white !important;
            padding: 8px 20px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s !important;
        }
        
        .admin-link:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(44,94,46,0.3);
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 140px 40px 80px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .hero { text-align: center; padding: 60px 0 40px; }
        .hero-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 8px 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(44,94,46,0.1), rgba(128,0,32,0.1));
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2C5E2E;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 64px;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #2C5E2E 40%, #800020 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
        .hero p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #475569;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 14px 35px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2C5E2E 0%, #800020 100%);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            margin: 0 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(44,94,46,0.3); }
        .btn-outline {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 14px 35px;
            background: transparent;
            border: 2px solid #2C5E2E;
            color: #2C5E2E;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            margin: 0 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .btn-outline:hover { background: #2C5E2E; color: white; transform: translateY(-2px); }
        
        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 25px;
            margin: 80px 0;
        }
        .stat-card {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 35px 25px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .stat-card:hover { transform: translateY(-8px); }
        .stat-number {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 800;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2C5E2E, #800020);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
        .stat-label { color: #64748b; font-weight: 500; margin-top: 10px; }
        
        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 38px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 60px 0 20px;
        }
        .section-title span { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2C5E2E, #800020); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
        .section-subtitle { text-align: center; color: #64748b; margin-bottom: 50px; font-size: 18px; }
        
        .services-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 25px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .service-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 35px 25px;
            border-radius: 24px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }
        .service-card:hover { transform: translateY(-8px); }
        .service-icon { font-size: 52px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .service-card h3 { font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .service-card p { color: #64748b; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 14px; }
        
        .cta-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #f1f5f9 100%);
            border-radius: 40px;
            padding: 60px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 60px 0;
        }
        .cta-section h2 { font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        
        .footer {
            background: #0f172a;
            color: white;
            padding: 60px 40px 30px;
            margin-top: 60px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .stats-grid, .services-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .hero h1 { font-size: 36px; }
            .container { padding: 120px 20px 60px; }
            .navbar { padding: 15px 20px; }
            .nav-links { gap: 15px; }
            .nav-links a { font-size: 14px; }
            .admin-link { padding: 5px 12px; font-size: 12px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="logo">Two Dee Engineering</div>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/services">Services</a>
            <a href="/projects">Projects</a>
            <a href="/about">About</a>
            <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
            <a href="/admin/login" class="admin-link">🔐 Admin</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="hero">
            <div class="hero-badge">✦ ENGINEERING TOMORROW ✦</div>
            <h1>Two Dee Engineering Servives.<br>Precision Engineering. Proven Results.</h1>
            <p>Structural, Electrical & Civil Engineering for complex commercial and residential projects.<br>Licensed in Texas and California.</p>
            <a href="/projects" class="btn-primary">Explore Projects</a>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-outline">Request Consultation</a>
        </div>

        <div class="stats-grid">
            <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-number">25+</div><div class="stat-label">Years Experience</div></div>
            <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-number">150+</div><div class="stat-label">Projects Completed</div></div>
            <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-number">100%</div><div class="stat-label">Client Satisfaction</div></div>
            <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-number">15</div><div class="stat-label">States Served</div></div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="section-title">Our <span>Expertise</span></h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Comprehensive engineering solutions tailored to your project needs</p>

        <div class="services-grid">
            <div class="service-card"><div class="service-icon">🏗️</div><h3>Structural Engineering</h3><p>Innovative structural design for commercial and residential buildings.</p></div>
            <div class="service-card"><div class="service-icon">🏞️</div><h3>Civil Engineering</h3><p>Site development, infrastructure, and environmental solutions.</p></div>
            <div class="service-card"><div class="service-icon">⚡</div><h3>MEP Engineering</h3><p>Mechanical, electrical, and plumbing systems design.</p></div>
            <div class="service-card"><div class="service-icon">🔧</div><h3>Construction Consulting</h3><p>Expert guidance throughout the construction lifecycle.</p></div>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-section">
            <h2>Ready to discuss your next project?</h2>
            <p>Let's bring your vision to life with precision engineering.</p>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Start Your Project →</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Two Dee Engineering Services. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 12px;">Licensed PE: TX-123456 | CA-789101</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
